%o A249152 (PARI) a(n) = sum(i=1, n, i*valuation(i, 2)); \\ _Michel Marcus_, Sep 14 2021
%o A249152 (PARI) a(n) = my(v=binary(n),t=0); forstep(j=#v,1,-1, if(v[j],v[j]=t--,t++)); (n^2 + fromdigits(v,2))>>1; \\ _Kevin Ryde_, Nov 03 2021
